36/**
37 * \file
38 *
39 * This file contains a module that performs DNS64 query processing.
40 */
41
42#ifndef DNS64_DNS64_H
43#define DNS64_DNS64_H
44#include "util/module.h"
45
46/**
47 * Get the dns64 function block.
48 * @return: function block with function pointers to dns64 methods.
49 */
50struct module_func_block *dns64_get_funcblock(void);
51
52/** dns64 init */
53int dns64_init(struct module_env* env, int id);
54
55/** dns64 deinit */
56void dns64_deinit(struct module_env* env, int id);
57
58/** dns64 operate on a query */
59void dns64_operate(struct module_qstate* qstate, enum module_ev event, int id,
60 struct outbound_entry* outbound);
61
62void dns64_inform_super(struct module_qstate* qstate, int id,
63 struct module_qstate* super);
64
65/** dns64 cleanup query state */
66void dns64_clear(struct module_qstate* qstate, int id);
67
68/** dns64 alloc size routine */
69size_t dns64_get_mem(struct module_env* env, int id);
70
71#endif /* DNS64_DNS64_H */
